<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Identity Automation</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study idauto">
    <header class="case-header overlay">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Identity Automation</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Making working together&nbsp;<br />simple and secure</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Identity Management Platform</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We created a unified product platform that gives users and administrators the right access to the right apps and the right data.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded gray">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            One UX for all
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We designed a platform that performs for users of all ages, from grade-school students and administrators to business owners and their employees.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A flexible, intuitive framework
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We simplified the platform’s structure to make it easier to manage software and data access across organizations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Front End Development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Navigating without having to think</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We designed an approach that anticipates and prioritizes based on what users need to do first, most, or almost never.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded-top column half-md red">
        <div class="container">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/single-mobile.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-bottom">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded dark-gray">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/duo-mobile-left.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/duo-mobile-right.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-bottom">
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column order-top-xs half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Unified under a common canvas</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              New modules and features don’t have to be built from scratch. A powerful underlying system of visual space can handle any combination of data that a user might need.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img src="./images/work/idauto/mobile-banner.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Engineered with an eye for detail</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We built the front-end in EmberJS, working with the client to define API functionality. We built not just an app, but the first step in a broader platform to serve future customers. And, the resulting code makes the design shine to the fullest.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column half-md idauto-code-phone">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/code-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/code-mobile.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute-bottom sr-bottom">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded red">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/duo-mobile-left-alt.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
          <img src="./images/work/idauto/duo-mobile-right-alt.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-bottom">
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column order-top-xs half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Bringing it to life</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Beautiful animations and visual feedback&mdash;progress bars, transitions, and validated input fields&mdash;make users feel in control, without wondering whether something worked.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md gray">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Working with their team has been nothing short of amazing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md dark-gray">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">It is rare to work with another company with the same passion for excellence as we have here at Identity Automation. We certainly see that same passion in Brave UX. Our experience working with their team has been nothing short of amazing. We are now seeing the fruits of their labor in our products today, and I am extremely happy with their work!</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Troy Moreland, <em>Founder &amp; CTO, Identity Automation</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/upfront" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
          <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/ijr" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>

    <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
